<p class="MsoNormal" style=" margin: 0 10">
<span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
Κ</span><span lang="EL" style=" ">ύριε, 
ἐλέησον</span><span lang="EL" style=" color: #C41E3A">(γ΄)</span><i><span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
</span></i>
<span lang="EL" style=" ">Πάτερ 
Ἅγιε εὐλόγησον.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style=" margin: 0 10">
<span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
