  <p class="MsoNormal" style=" margin: 0 10">
  <span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
  ΔΙΑΚΟΝΟΣ</span></p>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style=" margin: 0 10">
  <span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
  Ε</span><span lang="EL" style="">ἴπωμεν πάντες ἐξ ὅλης τῆς ψυχῆς καὶ ἐξ ὅλης τῆς διανοίας ἡμῶν εἴπωμεν</span><span style="">.</span></p>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style=" margin: 0 10">
  <span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
