<font color="#C41E3A" size="5">Ἀ</font>μήν. </span></p>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0 10">
  <span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
  Ε</span><span lang="EL" style="">ἴη τὸ ὄνομα 
