  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0 10">
  <span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
  Δ</span><span lang="EL" style="">όξα σοι, 
  Χριστὲ ὁ Θεός, ἡ ἐλπὶς ἡμῶν, δόξα σοι. </span></p>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style=" margin: 0 10">
  <span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
  ΧΟΡΟΣ</span></p>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style=" margin: 0 10">
