<span lang="EN-US" style="  color: #C41E3A">
&nbsp;Ἀ</span><span lang="EN-US" style=" ">μήν.
</span>
<span lang="EN-US" style="  color: #C41E3A">
Ἐ</span><span lang="EN-US" style=" ">ν 
ὀνόματι Κυρίου, εὐλόγησον, Πάτερ.</span></p>
