  <p class="MsoPlainText" style=" margin: 0 10px">
  <span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
  Τ</span><span lang="EL" style=" ">ῆς</span><span lang="EL" style=" ">
  </span>
  <span lang="EL" style="  letter-spacing: -.5pt">
  Παναγίας, ἀχράντου, ὑπερευλογημένης</span><span lang="EL" style=" ">, 
