</span>
<span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
(ἐκ γ')</span></p>
<p class="MsoPlainText" style=" margin: 0 10">
<span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
Στίχ. δ'. </span>
<span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
Π</span><span lang="EL" style=" ">ρόσθες 
αὐτοῖς κακά, Κύριε, πρόσθες αὐτοῖς κακά, τοῖς ἐνδόξοις τῆς γῆς.</span></p>
<p class="MsoPlainText" style="margin: 0 10">
<span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
Ἀ</span><span lang="EL" style="  color: black">λληλούϊα.
</span>
<span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
(ἐκ γ')</span></p>
<p class="MsoPlainText" align="center" style=" margin: 0 10">
<span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
Ἦχος πλ. δ'</span></p>
<p class="MsoPlainText" style=" margin: 0 10">
<span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
Ὅ</span><span lang="EL" style=" ">τε 
