καταφεύγομεν, ὡς ἄρρηκτον τεῖχος, καὶ προστασίαν. </span></p>
<p class="MsoPlainText" align="center" style=" margin: 0 10">
<span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
Κάθισμα</span><span lang="EL" style=" ">&nbsp;
<span style="color: #C41E3A">Ἦχος βαρὺς</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoPlainText" style=" margin: 0 10">
