</span>
<span lang="EL" style=" ">
Θεοτόκε Μαρία</span><span style=" ">,
</span>
<span lang="EL" style=" ">
πανύμνητε</span><span style=" ">,
</span>
<span lang="EL" style=" ">
καὶ ἀπειρόγαμε</span><span style=" ">.
