</span>
<span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
Ἦχος πλ</span><span style="  color: #C41E3A">.
</span>
<span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
β</span><span style="  color: #C41E3A">'</span></p>
<p class="MsoPlainText" style=" margin: 0 10">
<span lang="EL" style="  color: #C41E3A">
